question: What are the first 3 games played by the stream 'itsbigchase'?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream {name: 'itsbigchase'})-[:PLAYS]->(g:Game)
RETURN g.name AS game
ORDER BY s.createdAt
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $g isa game, has name $gn; (streaming_channel: $s, played_game: $g) isa game_play; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "game": $gn };

question: List the top 5 streams that have a total view count greater than 5000000.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)
WHERE s.total_view_count > 5000000
RETURN s.name AS stream_name, s.total_view_count AS view_count
ORDER BY s.total_view_count DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn, has total_view_count $v; sort $v desc; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "views": $v };

question: Which game is the most commonly played among the top 5 streams by follower count?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)-[:PLAYS]->(g:Game)
WITH g, s
ORDER BY s.followers DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN g.name AS game, count(*) AS count
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 1
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $g isa game, has name $gn; (streaming_channel: $s, played_game: $g) isa game_play; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "game": $gn };

question: Find the top 5 games played by streams that also chatter with other streams.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)-[:PLAYS]->(g:Game), (s)-[:CHATTER]->(:Stream)
WITH g, count(*) AS count
RETURN g.name AS game, count
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $g isa game, has name $gn; (streaming_channel: $s, played_game: $g) isa game_play; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "game": $gn };

question: What are the top 3 most recent streams to reach over 1 million followers?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)
WHERE s.followers > 1000000
RETURN s.name AS stream_name, s.createdAt AS created_at, s.followers
ORDER BY s.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn, has followers $f; sort $f desc; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "followers": $f };

question: Which 3 users are VIPs on the most diverse set of streams?
cypher:
MATCH (u:User)-[:VIP]->(s:Stream)
WITH u, count(distinct s) as num_streams
RETURN u.name, num_streams
ORDER BY num_streams DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $u isa user, has name $un; (channel_with_vips: $s, vip_user: $u) isa vip_status; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "vip": $un };

question: Which streams have a total view count over 1 million?
cypher:

WHERE s.total_view_count > 1000000
RETURN s.name, s.total_view_count
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn, has total_view_count $v; sort $v desc; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "views": $v };

question: List the games that have been played by more than five different streams.
cypher:
MATCH (g:Game)<-[:PLAYS]-(s:Stream)
WITH g, count(distinct s) as numStreams
WHERE numStreams > 5
RETURN g.name as game, numStreams
ORDER BY numStreams DESC
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $g isa game, has name $gn; (streaming_channel: $s, played_game: $g) isa game_play; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "game": $gn };

question: What are the names of users who are moderators for more than three streams?

MATCH (u:User)-[:MODERATOR]->(s:Stream)
WITH u, count(s) AS num_moderated_streams
WHERE num_moderated_streams > 3
RETURN u.name AS user_name
typeql: match $s1 isa stream, has name $n1; $s2 isa stream, has name $n2; (moderating_channel: $s1, moderated_channel: $s2) isa moderation; limit 5; fetch { "moderator": $n1, "moderated": $n2 };

question: Identify the streams that have the most moderators.

question: List the games played by streams with the lowest follower counts.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)-[:PLAYS]->(g:Game)
WHERE s.followers IS NOT NULL
WITH g, min(s.followers) AS minFollowers
MATCH (s2:Stream)-[:PLAYS]->(g)
WHERE s2.followers = minFollowers
RETURN g.name AS game, minFollowers AS lowestFollowerCount
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $g isa game, has name $gn; (streaming_channel: $s, played_game: $g) isa game_play; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "game": $gn };

MATCH (s:Stream)
WHERE s.followers IS NOT NULL AND s.total_view_count IS NOT NULL
RETURN s.name AS stream, toFloat(s.followers) / s.total_view_count AS follower_to_view_ratio
ORDER BY follower_to_view_ratio DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn, has followers $f; sort $f desc; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "followers": $f };

question: Find the top 5 streams by oldest to newest based on the 'createdAt' property.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)
WHERE s.createdAt IS NOT NULL
RETURN s
ORDER BY s.createdAt
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn };

question: Which 3 languages are least common among streams with more than 10,000 followers?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)-[:HAS_LANGUAGE]->(l:Language)
WHERE s.followers > 10000
WITH l, count(*) as count
ORDER BY count
LIMIT 3
RETURN l.name as language, count
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $l isa language, has name $ln; (channel: $s, used_language: $l) isa language_usage; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "language": $ln };

question: List the top 5 users who have the role of chatter in the highest number of other user's streams.
cypher:
MATCH (u:User)-[:CHATTER]->(s:Stream)<-[:CHATTER]-(other:User)
WHERE u <> other
WITH u, count(distinct s) as chatter_count
ORDER BY chatter_count DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN u.name as user, chatter_count
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $u isa user, has name $un; (channel_with_chatters: $s, chatting_user: $u) isa chat_activity; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "user": $un };

question: What are the three most common teams that streams belong to?

ORDER BY num_streams DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $t isa team, has name $tn; (member_stream: $s, organization: $t) isa team_membership; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "team": $tn };

question: List the 3 streams where the streamer has the longest ongoing stream based on the creation date.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)
RETURN s.name AS stream_name, s.createdAt AS created_at
ORDER BY s.createdAt
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn };

question: Show the top 5 streams with the most user chatters.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)<-[:CHATTER]-(u:User)
RETURN s.name AS stream, count(u) AS chatter_count
ORDER BY chatter_count DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $u isa user, has name $un; (channel_with_chatters: $s, chatting_user: $u) isa chat_activity; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "user": $un };

question: Find 3 streams with the most varied language settings.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)-[:HAS_LANGUAGE]->(l:Language)
WITH s, count(distinct l) as numLanguages
ORDER BY numLanguages DESC
LIMIT 3
RETURN s.name as streamName, numLanguages
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $l isa language, has name $ln; (channel: $s, used_language: $l) isa language_usage; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "language": $ln };

question: Which streams have a user as both a VIP and a MODERATOR?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)<-[:VIP]-(u:User)-[:MODERATOR]->(s)
RETURN s.name AS stream, u.name AS user
typeql: match $s1 isa stream, has name $n1; $s2 isa stream, has name $n2; (moderating_channel: $s1, moderated_channel: $s2) isa moderation; limit 5; fetch { "moderator": $n1, "moderated": $n2 };

question: What are the first 5 streams that have the most chatters?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)<-[:CHATTER]-()
RETURN s.name AS stream, count(*) AS chatter_count
ORDER BY chatter_count DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $u isa user, has name $un; (channel_with_chatters: $s, chatting_user: $u) isa chat_activity; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "user": $un };

question: List the streams that play a game named 'Just Chatting' and have more than 100,000 followers.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)-[:PLAYS]->(g:Game {name: 'Just Chatting'})
WHERE s.followers > 100000
RETURN s
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $g isa game, has name $gn; (streaming_channel: $s, played_game: $g) isa game_play; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "game": $gn };

question: Which streams are part of a team with the most streams associated?
cypher:
MATCH (t:Team)<-[:HAS_TEAM]-(s:Stream)
WITH t, count(s) AS stream_count
ORDER BY stream_count DESC
LIMIT 1
MATCH (t)<-[:HAS_TEAM]-(stream:Stream)
RETURN stream
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $t isa team, has name $tn; (member_stream: $s, organization: $t) isa team_membership; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "team": $tn };

question: Show the top 5 users who are VIPs in the most streams.
cypher:
MATCH (u:User)-[:VIP]->(s:Stream)
WITH u, count(s) AS vip_count
ORDER BY vip_count DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN u.name AS user, vip_count
typeql: match $s isa stream, has name $sn; $u isa user, has name $un; (channel_with_vips: $s, vip_user: $u) isa vip_status; limit 5; fetch { "stream": $sn, "vip": $un };

question: Who are the top 3 moderators in the stream with the lowest follower count?
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)<-[:MODERATOR]-(m:User)
WITH s, m
ORDER BY s.followers ASC, count{(m)-[:MODERATOR]->(s)} DESC
LIMIT 1
WITH s
MATCH (s)<-[:MODERATOR]-(moderator:User)
RETURN moderator.name AS moderator, moderator.followers AS followers
ORDER BY followers DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $s1 isa stream, has name $n1; $s2 isa stream, has name $n2; (moderating_channel: $s1, moderated_channel: $s2) isa moderation; limit 5; fetch { "moderator": $n1, "moderated": $n2 };
